<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>It looks like a picture graph.</li>
      <li>There is no title.</li>
      <li>The categories are hidden.</li>
      <li>There are stick people in each column.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>What is this graph about?</li>
      <li>What do the stick people represent?</li>
      <li>Why are there so many stick people in the last two columns?</li>
      <li>Where is the title?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


