      <li>Math Community: Ask students to reflect on both individual and group actions while considering the question
        <q>¿Qué ven y qué escuchan cuando hacemos matemáticas juntos como una comunidad matemática?, ¿qué estoy haciendo yo?, ¿qué están haciendo ustedes?</q> (We talked to each other and to the teacher. We had quiet time to think. We shared our ideas. We thought about the math ideas and words we knew. You were writing down our answers. You were waiting until we gave the answers.)
